# Keep the Docker build context small + secret-free. The Dockerfile COPYs explicit paths anyway; this
# mainly speeds the context upload and guarantees node_modules/dist/.env never leak into an image layer.
**/node_modules
**/dist
.git
.github
**/*.log
**/.env
.env
spikes/data
spikes/out
docs
tools
infra
charts
**/*.md
